{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Death Fortress&quot; is an action Rogue lite game. A secret experiment created you, as a terrible biological weapon of the empire, you are reborn from pain, will you kill all your enemies or complete your revenge. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">1. Defeat the enemy with one strike, enjoy the battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform into an agile and ruthless killer, and every strike can bring the pleasure of one-hit-kill, and the battle experience is refreshing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475190/extras/1.gif?t=1739522109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">2. Rich content, never get tired of playing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than 400 ability enhancements, more than 50 skill upgrades, multiple ability combinations to unlock powerful bonds and unlock suits. Randomly generated maps, new challenges every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475190/extras/2.gif?t=1739522109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">3. Permanent reinforcement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill and collect the blood of your enemies to permanently strengthen your abilities and unlock new props and equipment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">4. Control the power of space and time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a powerful bio-weapon, you have the power to manipulate time and space. Not only can you change the speed of time, but you can even bounce back bullets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3475190/extras/3.gif?t=1739522109\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">5. Unique pixel art</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The perfect combination of real materials and pixel images brings a brand new pixel style art experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akam